We have not taken the aBOT offline for any updates since its release and it is now time to give the backend some very important upgrades. At least 72 hours before aBOT becomes live again, we will announce and release all the aBOT gas information, provide guides and several "how to videos". I kindly ask you all to please be patient while we complete this very important process. We will do everything in our power to ensure everything is back to normal as soon as possible. Keep in mind, this aBOT upgrade will not effect the function of the Internal Exchange and all other platform features will function as normal.  Thank you for your continued support, Thomas Brown
